Title: The Birthday Party
Plot: Earl wants to use his birthday to look back on all the good he's done over the past year, but at his party, everyone seems to want to talk about his past misdeeds instead.
GuestStars: Trey Carlisle,  Juan Pope,  Beau Bridges,  Silas Weir Mitchell,  Abdoulaye N'Gom,  Phoenix  Smith,  Bill Suplee
